## What you need to modify

Your project has 9 files. You only need to care about 4:

| File | What it does | When to edit |
|------|-------------|-------------|
| `lib/app/` | App routing and providers | **Every time** |
| `lib/` (your feature folders) | Feature screens and logic | **Every time** |
| `test/` | Tests for your features | **Every time** |
| `lib/main.dart` | App entry point | Rarely |
| Others (android/, ios/, pubspec.yaml) | Platform config | Almost never |

